Class HDBOfficer

Object
User
Applicant
HDBOfficer
public class HDBOfficer extends Applicant
Represents an HDB Officer in the Build-To-Order system. Inherits from Applicant and includes additional functionality to handle project registration and assignment logic specific to officers. Officers can register for multiple projects, but may only be actively assigned to one. Each project has a registration status tracked using an internal map. Status values include:
  • NOT_REGISTERED
  • PENDING
  • APPROVED
  • REJECTED
Version:
1.0
Author:
Javier
